reviewText: David Wilhite is a bore.  This tape is a sedative.  If you know ANYTHING about the game of craps, you probably won't learn much more from this tape.  Better to buy a good book on it AND play a computer game to hone your skills before going to the casino with your real money.  Speaking of real money, don't waste it on this tape!
What a great video!  Very educational and lots of tips and tricks I hadn't even thought of.
